Authorities are investigating after the 25-year-old man's body was found along the roadway on Sunday. CAPE TOWN - Khayelitsha police are investigating the discovery of a body dumped near Baden Powell Drive.The 25-year-old man's body was found along the roadway on Sunday.He had been stabbed to death.The police's Andre Traut says: Any person with information regarding the matter is urged to contact Crime Stop at 08600 10111. (Edited by Shimoney Regter)